# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# .gitattributes — Binary/text handling for poland-food-db
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Binary image assets — mark as binary for correct diff behavior
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary

# SVG — treat as text for diffs (they're XML)
*.svg text

# Font files
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary

# Design source files (if ever added)
*.fig binary
*.sketch binary
*.psd binary
*.ai binary
